<p>
  Grants voice to a user (prefix +), allowing them to speak in moderated (+m) channels. Half-operators and above can grant voice.
</p>
<.help_h4 icon={:icon_terminal}>Usage</.help_h4>
<pre>/mode +v Alice    — Give voice to Alice
/mode -v Alice    — Remove voice from Alice</pre>
<.help_h4 icon={:icon_link}>See Also</.help_h4>
<p>
  <.help_link topic="mode-m">Moderated (+m)</.help_link>
  · <.help_link topic="mode-h">Half-Operator (+h)</.help_link>
</p>
